Vleigh Place, north from near 72nd Avenue. The house shown on the left was owned, according to Mr. Armbruster, by H. Van

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection    1925

728176f-a.text:
71-66 Vleigh Place, east side, near 72nd Avenue, showing one of the few remaining old homesteads of this area. The house and a 10-acre farm was owned by Mrs. Gotman in 1909.

P. L. Sperr                   March 3, 1937
